pl.sudokusolver.recognizerlib.sudoku

Class BaseSudokuExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.sudokusolver.recognizerlib.sudoku.SudokuExtractor
      • pl.sudokusolver.recognizerlib.sudoku.BaseSudokuExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISudokuExtractor

    public class BaseSudokuExtractor
extends SudokuExtractor
    Base sudoku extractor controller.
    Extraction algorithm:
    • Apply preGridFilters to input matrix
    • Using gridExtractStrategy extracting grid
    • Apply preCellsFilters to grid
    • For each cell apply preDigitsFilters to send output to recognizer
